"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-news-london-paris-olympics-eurostar-golden-trains-team-gb-st-pancras-spectators-b1166673.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News|London  Get our award-winning daily news email featuring exclusive stories, opinion and expert analysis    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"London 2012 Olympic champion Jessica Ennis-Hill has helped Eurostar to unveil two \\\"golden trains\\\" that will transport athletes and spectators to the Paris Games this summer.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 448, \"end\": 459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999996721272, \"rank\": 3.2772223048896687e-10, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 477, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Ennis-Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\"}, {\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999987433644657, \"rank\": 1.25663710455225e-06, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cross-channel high-speed rail firm is an official partner to Team GB and aims to transport 2,000 athletes and staff - including from Team Belgium, Team Netherlands, and Team Germany - and two million spectators to the French capital for the Olympics and Paralympics.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.999999905282043, \"rank\": 9.43977187716516e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9365558939199611, \"rank\": 0.06675129801891358, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.9993799493339206, \"rank\": 0.0006204353675087652, \"text\": \"Team Netherlands\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_baseball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.999647026088968, \"rank\": 0.0003530899136221478, \"text\": \"Team Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.737430831633402, \"rank\": 0.31510180595898496, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The newly-decorated e320 trains were unveiled with one month to go until the start of the Games.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dame Jess, who won the heptathlon gold in 2012, was joined at St Pancras on Tuesday morning by Paralympics GB double gold medallist Maisie Summers-Newton - who will compete this summer - and former Team GB athlete Perri Shakes-Drayton.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1207, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perri_Shakes-Drayton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Perri Shakes-Drayton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perri_Shakes-Drayton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perri_Shakes-Drayton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Up to eight extra services a day will run at peak times on July 25 to 27 and August 10-12, periods that overlap with the opening and closing ceremonies of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Train tickets are still available.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An Olympic \\\"fan zone\\\" is being set up at Coal Drops Yard, near St Pancras station.\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coal_Drops_Yard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coal Drops Yard\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coal_Drops_Yard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coal_Drops_Yard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dame Jessica said: \\\"Eurostar's golden train symbolises the journey towards excellence.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1524, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9987777196805476, \"rank\": 0.0011121636470820743, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}, {\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999987433644657, \"rank\": 1.25663710455225e-06, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an honour to be part of this launch, and I wish all the athletes the best as they compete on the world stage as I pass the baton to\\u00a0talent such as Maisie.\\\"\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simon Lejeune, Eurostar chief safety and stations officer, said: \\\"Today marks the launch of one month to go to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1783, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999987433644657, \"rank\": 1.25663710455225e-06, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eurostar is delighted to partner with four national teams for Paris 2024 including Team GB and Paralympics GB.\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1893, \"end\": 1901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999987433644657, \"rank\": 1.25663710455225e-06, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 1976, \"end\": 1983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.999999905282043, \"rank\": 9.43977187716516e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1988, \"end\": 2002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Paralympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympics GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Paralympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Paralympic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In honour of this, we have launched the golden train,\\u00a0a symbol of support for all athletes going for gold and for customers who will be travelling via us to get to the Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicte